Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.22,0:00:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen-sama, please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't die!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.46,0:01:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1070,0,0.3,\c&HEFF8F7&\3c&HEFF8F7&\4c&HEFF8F7&)}Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.63,0:01:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.97,0:01:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have finals starting today!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't studied at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.89,0:01:52.52,Announcer,,0,0,0,,The death toll from the last month's earthquake off the coast of Wales has reached 1,263.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.52,0:01:55.77,Announcer,,0,0,0,,Natural disasters have been hitting all parts of the globe this year.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.77,0:01:59.82,Announcer,,0,0,0,,Earthquakes, tsunamis, volcanic eruptions,\N and freak weather conditions
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.62,Announcer,,0,0,0,,have already claimed over 20,000 lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.60,Announcer,,0,0,0,,The number of large cities decimated by these disasters is now eight.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.09,Announcer,,0,0,0,,With rebuilding efforts stalling, \Nevery nation has been forced
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.09,0:02:13.91,Announcer,,0,0,0,,to take emergency measures \Nagainst these continuing natural disasters.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.91,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Hazumi-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tsu, nu, ri, tari form...'' {https://homura-study.com/classical-literature-auxiliary-verb-tu-nu-tari-ri/ - apparently, some auxiliary verbs from old japanese}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Hazumi-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.53,0:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting on!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.17,0:03:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! I can't take any more\N finals in a place like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't solve any more problems.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.28,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a right to complain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's our Hazumi for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The number one school destroyer in Japan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sowwy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The first session's finally over?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I flunked both Modern Japanese and Math.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No use grumbling about it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do your best tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so positive, Yuka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have to go. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun again?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You two really are close.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then. Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just siblings who are really close?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, darn, it sucks that we're siblings, even though we're not related.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.22,0:04:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I should just confess\N to Takumi and be done with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.86,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A white chapel, a white carriage,\N and a white wedding dress!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.25,0:04:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the two of us...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! Oh, Takumi...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something really good happen to you, Hazumi-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be that you nailed today's exams!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a disaster.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.59,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do better if you bothered to study.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.54,0:04:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! When we get home, let's study English together. I'll spend the rest of the day with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.50,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Takumi, I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better do that, Hazumi-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacore shadow-print panties, size M. {was "Racole" originally, but I think this sounds better since both are a guess}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got perfect childbearing hips, Hazumi-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always up to the same thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Takumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hazumi-kun, you're not getting any summer vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.52,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail any of your exams, you'll spend \Nthe whole summer in a supplementary school.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Supplementary school?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Camping, going to the sea, \Nthe amusement park.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.89,0:05:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd actually spend my summer vacation \Ndoing all those things with Takumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Takumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. No more joking around, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the joke around here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to do here now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to return home and study.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Takumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.88,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a basketball meeting this afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But it's finals week.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.70,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's an emergency meeting, \Naccording to our manager, Hime-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.18,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Takumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.61,0:06:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to study as hard\N as you can, Hazumi-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.43,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Takumi! Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got herself involved in a painful battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.07,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope the main trouble waits \Nat least until finals are over.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When will we have to face the Dark World?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In another few days.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be here within a week, at the latest.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan, where is everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"P-Particularly."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokuni.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Take care of."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.68,0:07:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sewa o suru.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.37,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Difficult. Diffi... Difficult..."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is stuff is difficult!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.45,0:07:36.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,I won't let some summer school ruin\N my summer vacation with Takumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,Being siblings...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,Really, it's such a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.88,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, what was that for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.73,0:08:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then, what did you draw it for?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.38,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe it's a dead end\N right now, but someday...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I'll tell him the truth,\N and we'll get married!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi is your brother!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.28,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a more important duty \Nthan chasing empty dreams like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember. Protect Takumi, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.85,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to finals, \Nfighting the Remnants is a walk in the park!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.44,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to realize yet how difficult it will be\N to keep protecting Takumi until the very end.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hime-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You shouldn't be doing that, Hime-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun, I'm giving you...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.99,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,all of my body!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.33,0:09:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll suppress the altar \Nand then slaughter all the Guardians!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.42,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you eliminate the Key, Jinno Takumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amore, amore, amore mio! {"Love, love, ah, my love!" originally, I don't think these words are obscure enough to translate it}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A Remnant!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.78,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonjour, Mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.52,0:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For thirty-five years, \NI have been seducing beautiful ladies.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.02,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And by my name of Michel Yamada, I thank God\N for finally letting me meet you, mon amour!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,S'il vous plaît!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.87,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bah! Cut the crap now and get out of our way!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.38,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame, I won't let you go tonight. Yes, tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is disgusting! {nc whats first word}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.11,0:09:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hazumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.92,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you two look good together.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving him to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to save Takumi! Later!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join us too, Mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.39,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Madame had been so gentle with me before{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Hurry up to save Takumi, Hazumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've found somebody middle-aged like you. Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.64,0:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Middle-aged?! Who are you calling that? You ungrateful...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi, I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards! Who permitted you to enter here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.11,0:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Remnants are prohibited\N from the school grounds!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you read this rules\N book even once?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found you, my boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all to Lady Aoi's credit.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away today!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I wouldn't take another step.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.36,0:11:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're handsome, even if you're a Guardian.\N I'll give you a score of 83.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've passed my test, boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm truly pleased.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the gaudy old bags can be nice sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Old bag? Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.38,0:11:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You rude son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.66,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, je t'aime! Are you hurt somewhere, Madame? Oui.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You French swine!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a taste\N of a Japanese housewife's power!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Housewife's Osakan Kitchen Knife Fire! {nc, but houzenji yokocho could be https://www.kanpai-japan.com/osaka/hozenji-yokocho}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.19,0:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still pretty easy to make advances to the madames of Japan! {nc whats juu, prolly another french buzzword}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.75,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Housewife's Perfectly Cooked Noodles! {nc whatsoever this time, but she says "koshi is life" and koshi is how she later refers to herself, nc what it means since we know she's kasumi}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use fighting.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.35,0:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Jinno family secret handmade noodles.\N Be quiet now!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.51,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Madame, you are so strong, \Nand that's why you are my mon amour.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Je t'aime!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll defend it from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,But please, take care of Takumi, the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan, are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.94,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrettably, your game is over now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrettable indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wearing trousers. {nc, prolly means this as can be regrettable}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.31,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime, Takumi-kun, keep close to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good, dammit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.99,0:13:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! My brakes gave out!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kazuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't think I'll make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.84,0:13:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor, Hazumi. \NG-Give me one last kiss... kiss... kiss.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.73,0:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.71,0:13:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi's fine. He made his getaway.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks, Kazuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in a better shape now,\N I'd hug you too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi went to the docks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.74,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime's with him, so don't w{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime's with him?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.16,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my fairy tale.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you play with me in this fairy tale \Ntill morning, Madame?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, you pervert! \NKeep that nonsense to yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dealing with an Edoite, \Nand we've no time for sissies!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.89,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Non, non, Madame. \NNo, I mean, Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your passionate eyes,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,your sweet lips,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,your shining auburn hair.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.65,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were a flower, \Nyou'd indeed be this deep red rose!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.62,0:14:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this rose, Mademoiselle, \NI was growing it to dedicate to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shit! {nc}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How low can you go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the life of a gigolo, Madame!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The color of this rose is pure red, \Nlike human blood!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us darken the petals further!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.70,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This Japanese housewife will not lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.72,0:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret Technique: Ethnic Champ!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabasco!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow-ow-ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Real Wasabi!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Pepper!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch-ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Topped off by Hundredfold Hot Curry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry! It's curry! Curry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jinno Family Secret: Kasumi Special.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.62,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.78,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. All those Remnants flocked around Chiryuu-senpai, so we should be safe here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there Remnants even here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.64,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the advent of\N the Dark World is really close!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan special:
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-Wow Punch!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hime-chan, this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered something from when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like hide-and-seek. \N I used to play it with my neighbor, Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kijima Touta!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinno Takumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the reincarnation of Kairen.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.45,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?\N I won't let you live if you touch Takumi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.65,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To prevent the gate from ever being closed again, Kairen...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.06,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Bird Attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.73,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.36,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive anyone who hurts Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.74,0:18:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power is like an elementary school kid's.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.54,0:18:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your abilities don't match your large physique. {lit: you're an empty/worthless worst man who only relies on his body}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now freeze! {nc}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For such a cute girl, \Nyou sure have a foul mouth.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Slimeball.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.02,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That cool air sure feels\N good and refreshing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't you go out with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I need an air conditioner.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna play brave?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.37,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the winter, we'll have to break up, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's my alimony check!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Christ, it's frozen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She was damn good for a villain.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.22,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi, hang on!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.68,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Now you've pissed me off, you hear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.23,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly Lord Stroke: Comet Tornado Drop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.92,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.95,0:20:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.55,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping your Soul \Nmight've grown up a bit since then.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.94,0:20:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'll just break you down,\N along with the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's just like in my morning dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.71,0:20:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Stop this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't die!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally remembered your previous life.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My previous life?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason why I must kill you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.75,0:21:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen, I will kill you\N before you can throw yourself in.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to close the gate now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the cost, I will...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,protect Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.48,0:21:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect Takumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.80,0:21:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I will obtain the vengeance \NI have sought for 30,000 years.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle. Groan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink fully of your humiliation!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.64,0:22:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, the world will be\N enveloped in darkness.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.19,0:22:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How can you still stand?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.75,0:22:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you lay a single finger on Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.51,0:23:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way someone like you \Ncould possess such power!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.84,0:23:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.14,0:23:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.11,0:23:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.14,0:24:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In a battle, you don't know \Nwhat might happen until the very end!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.90,0:24:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is the true end!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.19,0:24:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.51,0:24:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.65,0:24:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.88,0:24:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:02.28,0:25:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.96,0:25:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Hazumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.48,0:25:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to close the gate and seal off the Dark World, I, the Key, must sacrifice myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:15.65,0:25:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.65,0:25:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairen-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.17,0:25:24.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,He's got to die to be the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.51,0:25:28.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,In order to seal off the gate, the Key...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.08,0:25:30.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,Takumi has to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.16,0:25:39.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,Takumi has to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:39.68,0:25:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:40.83,0:25:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.91,0:25:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:50.79,0:25:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi! Don't die!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.73,0:26:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi, you don't need to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.40,0:26:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:08.85,0:26:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.58,0:26:10.85,Alt,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.33,0:26:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi! You don't need to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.80,0:26:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, \NI will protect you with my life!
