Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.84,0:26:47.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now Hazumi and Takumi once again have to face\N their cruel fate from 30,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.97,0:26:55.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With all her power gone, \Nwill Hazumi be able to protect Takumi now?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:16.34,0:29:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.92,0:29:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody say it's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:20.01,0:29:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi is fated to die.\N I'll never let that happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:24.15,0:29:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to my Soul \Nat such an important time?!
